-# coding: utf-8

%div#toolbox_spacer_top
%div#toolbox
  %div 表示： 機器一覧
  %div
    条件：
    &= cond
  %div
    選択：
    %button#select_on_all すべて選択
    %button#select_off_all 選択をクリア
    %button#selected_bricks 選択対象のみ表示
    %button#bricks_history 変更履歴
  %div
    機器名で絞り込み: 
    %select#brick_selection_list
      %option{:selected => selected.nil?, :value => ''} すべて
      - products.each do |product|
        %option{:selected => (product == selected)}
          &= product
  - if @isadmin
    = haml :bricks_operations
%div#toolbox_spacer_bottom
%div#maincontents
  %table#bricklist
    = haml :brick_list, :locals => {:brick_list => @bricks}
